---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure"
  description="How Australian Home Collective handles affiliate links."
>
  <header class="page-intro">
    <div class="narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">Disclosure</p>
      <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Some pages may contain affiliate links. If you buy through one of these links,
        Australian Home Collective may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section class="content narrow">
    <p>
      Affiliate links help support the site and allow us to keep the guides practical, clean
      and focused on useful home decisions rather than filling pages with intrusive ads or
      pop-ups.
    </p>

    <h2>How this affects guides</h2>
    <p>
      Our aim is to help readers compare product types, features, storage ideas and everyday
      home setup options before deciding what suits their household. Affiliate links do not
      change that purpose.
    </p>

    <h2>Reader choice</h2>
    <p>
      You are never required to use our links. Before buying, check the retailer's current
      product information, price, delivery details, returns policy and suitability for your
      household.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
